data.title: On Oracle Corporation
data.meta_description: ppt on oracle corporation - Free download as Powerpoint Presentation (.ppt / .pptx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The acquisition of Sun Microsystems by Oracle was completed by Oracle on January 27, 2010. Oracle is an American multinational computer technology corporation that specializes in developing and marketing computer hardware systems and enterprise software products. Each acquisition contributed to Oracle's strategy of providing solutions rather than products to its customers.
